<title>SOUTH AFRICA: S.Africa's Harmony says to acquire Lydex.</title>
<headline>S.Africa's Harmony says to acquire Lydex.</headline>
<dateline>JOHANNESBURG 1996-11-03</dateline>
<text>
<p>South Africa's Harmony Gold Mining Co Ltd announced on Sunday an agreement had been reached for it to acquire control of Lydenburg Exploration Ltd.</p>
<p>The Johannesburg Stock Exchange had agreed to suspend the listing of Lydex until the start of business on Tuesday when further information would be made available to shareholders, Harmony said in a statement.</p>
